  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Kemotaku\" is a brand new card game mixed with puzzle, deck building and tower-defence.<br>You can choose 4 main characters, and the game features a wide variety of animal cards, skills, and items.<br>Enjoy deep gaming experiences with your own style.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/17fea1e2c53a7d9bf32f547775be9e33.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/17fea1e2c53a7d9bf32f547775be9e33.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=340 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐶Defend your town from attacking enemies!🐱</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To successfully defend your town, your allies' power must exceed the enemies' power.<br>You can gain power using cards, skills, and items.<br>Stand up to attacking enemies and keep up your health points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/7c313e9c825bfa78bad902c935cf0f86.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/7c313e9c825bfa78bad902c935cf0f86.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐼Stack animal cards to boost your power!🐻</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each animal card comes with fruits, and you can stack them if their fruits match. <br>Each time you stack cards, The power is boosted up and you can defeat high-power enemies. <br>And as your trust levels increase, more powerful animals can join the battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/e930ddd1497ee28f41acf5bcfa2fef06.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/e930ddd1497ee28f41acf5bcfa2fef06.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐺Match fruits and trigger skills!🐷</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 4 main characters have their own skills. <br>When animal cards are played and fruits match, skills are activated.<br>Triggering skills is very important to beat the game.<br>There are 48 skills per character and you can build your own skill deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/96887f3cd6769de4d8dba00bfd17c7d3.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/96887f3cd6769de4d8dba00bfd17c7d3.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐵Fresh gaming experience every time!🐹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many enemies and bosses against you.<br>Every boss has strong skills and use them every turn.<br>If you can't deal with them well, you'll be defeated.<br>And the game features many events, items and a card upgrading system.<br>You can enjoy it again and again with fresh feelings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/aa4a25f58cbc611a45f68a145df1bd1a.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/aa4a25f58cbc611a45f68a145df1bd1a.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/9c1f1e43b1fb3693a3d6d60ba0e1dbee.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/9c1f1e43b1fb3693a3d6d60ba0e1dbee.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/cda372e37ee404c4e2258975fbeed9a2.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/cda372e37ee404c4e2258975fbeed9a2.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐨Human Translations!🐧</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I translated all game texts from Japanese to English by myself, not machine translations.<br>If you find any weird parts, let me know.<br>I will fix it as soon as possible.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Kemotaku\" is a brand new card game mixed with puzzle, deck building and tower-defence.<br>You can choose 4 main characters, and the game features a wide variety of animal cards, skills, and items.<br>Enjoy deep gaming experiences with your own style.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/17fea1e2c53a7d9bf32f547775be9e33.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/17fea1e2c53a7d9bf32f547775be9e33.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=340 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐶Defend your town from attacking enemies!🐱</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To successfully defend your town, your allies' power must exceed the enemies' power.<br>You can gain power using cards, skills, and items.<br>Stand up to attacking enemies and keep up your health points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/7c313e9c825bfa78bad902c935cf0f86.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/7c313e9c825bfa78bad902c935cf0f86.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐼Stack animal cards to boost your power!🐻</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each animal card comes with fruits, and you can stack them if their fruits match. <br>Each time you stack cards, The power is boosted up and you can defeat high-power enemies. <br>And as your trust levels increase, more powerful animals can join the battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/e930ddd1497ee28f41acf5bcfa2fef06.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://