ras_big/9c1f1e43b1fb3693a3d6d60ba0e1dbee.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/cda372e37ee404c4e2258975fbeed9a2.avif?t=1771547916\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras_big/cda372e37ee404c4e2258975fbeed9a2.avif?t=1771547916 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐨Human Translations!🐧</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I translated all game texts from Japanese to English by myself, not machine translations.<br>If you find any weird parts, let me know.<br>I will fix it as soon as possible.</p>",
